1 Sourdough Loaf
1 tomato
½ packet pulled chicken
1 packet Dill & Parsley Mayonnaise
1 bag salad leaves
1 packet Smoked Cheddar Cheese

Thickly slice sourdough loaf. Thinly slice tomato. Discard liquid from pulled chicken packaging. In a medium bowl, combine pulled chicken (see ingredients), smoked Cheddar cheese and 1/2 the dill & parsley mayonnaise. Season with salt and pepper.

Spread remaining dill & parsley mayonnaise over sourdough slices. Layer a slice with pulled chicken mixture, tomato and salad leaves. Top with remaining sourdough slice.

Wrap sandwich in foil or plastic wrap.